divs: Sighting DetailsI was watching the movie "Go Figure" when I glanced out the window and saw colored fuzzy circles circling around a single spot.The circles alternated colors in this order:pink,green,purple,blue.When I first looked out the window I thought it was my uncle shooting a beam of light in the sky,but I realized he was in his house.They circles seemed to mov.but at the same time,seemed to occasionally teleport.Then it headed in the opposite direction,and beamed off in that direction.I was compelled to be near the UFO,and I once took a quiz by Dr. Marilyn Ruben in a book that told me I have been abducted but didn't know it.
Summary: Large colored fuzzy circles began circling arounda single spot in the sky.
